## Common Questions

### â€œWhich framework should I start with?â€

â†’ **TEGR** â€” itâ€™s the novel one. GR is reference.

### â€œWhatâ€™s a good Î“ value to test?â€

â†’ Try **Î“ = 0.35** â€” near stretched horizon but numerically stable.

### â€œHow long does a sweep take?â€

â†’ 30 steps Ã— 150 PDE ticks/step = ~5 seconds on modern hardware.

### â€œCan I compare TEGR vs GR directly?â€

â†’ **Yes!** Thatâ€™s the whole point. Run sweep in TEGR, toggle to GR, run again, compare exports.

### â€œIs the statistical test rigorous?â€

